data.description: Welcome home to the wonderful 55+ community of Cranberry Creek Estates. This three bedroom/ two and a half bath is a must see! There are hardwood floors throughout the downstairs with a large formal dining room as well as an eat-in kitchen with a stainless-steel appliance package. The spacious living room contains a gas fireplace. For convenience the master bedroom is downstairs. The master bath is apportioned with a jacuzzi jet tub, shower and double vanity. The back porch is covered and has a four seasons room off of it. Being sold in “as is” condition. HOA fee includes common area maintenance, health club, lawn care, pool, recreation facility and snow removal. Amenities include lounge area, club house, community center, exercise room, game room and pool. An ADT system is already wired in. Just need to start service. This is a short sale and is contingent upon third party approval. Being sold in as is condition. Buyer is responsible at their sole expense, for any repairs, inspections or certifications necessary to settle.
